name: SearchCriteria
description: Represents the search criteria to be used.

properties.name: completeMatch
properties.description: Specifies whether the match needs to be complete or partial. Default is false (partial).

properties.name: matchCase
properties.description: Specifies whether the match is case sensitive. Default is false (insensitive).

properties.name: searchDirection
properties.description: Specifies the search direction. Default is forward.
